import React, {useState} from 'react'
import {Sidebar, Menu, Icon} from 'semantic-ui-react'

export default function MenuSidebar() {
    const [visible,setVisible] = useState(false)
    
    
    return (
        <Sidebar
        as={Menu}
        animation='overlay'
        icon='labeled'
        inverted
        onHide={() => setVisible(false)}
        vertical
        visible={visible}
        width='thin'
      >
        <Menu.Item as='a'>
          <Icon name='home' />
          Home
        </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item as='a'>
          <Icon name='heart' />
          About Me
        </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item as='a'>
          <Icon name='folder' />
          Projects
        </Menu.Item>
      </Sidebar>)
}
